  "title": "Product Engineer (Test Development)***",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Final test yield enhancement, cycle time reduction, and quality improvement.</li><li>Daily engineering debug activities.</li><li>Documentation for product manufacturability.</li><li>Using sound technical judgment to support lot-on-hold disposition.</li><li>Produce yield and pareto reports per requirements.</li><li>Facilitate testing and shipment of both NPI and Sustaining devices.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Electrical/Electronics Engineering, or comparable disciplines</li><li>Working experience in ATE Test patterns, flows, debug using Adventest V93K</li></ul><p><br />Ethos Search Associates Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 13C6655</p><p>EA Reg No: R1988580 Jacky Chong</p>",
